name: Vik Shaffer
description: I am a very kind and sensitive person.I have a big heart.My friends can tell you that there is no woman so kind, tender,intelligent,honest,loving,caring and well-educated like I am.I am a woman who has his own principles and values.I believe that most of things in our life depend on us.I have my own aims and goals.I will do my best to achieve all that.I am a woman who loves children very much.I will be a good mother cause i am family oriented waiting patiently to have my kids someday.Marriage for me is the paradise for a family.If love and kindness,mutuality and sincerity were the cornerstones for creating the family wife and husband would have a long and happy life together.
